data.description: Gorgeous and completely renovated 2-story 2 bedroom townhouse with large loft that can be easily converted into 3rd bedroom.  Inground pool and NO HOA FEES.  Roof replaced in 2021 with architectural shingles.  Other recent renovations include:  All new kitchen and baths, new flooring throughout.  New HVAC system, electrical panel, pool pump and filter.  Fully applianced kitchen with pass through to dining area.  Washer & dryer inside.  One bedroom on first level.  Completely private and fenced rear patio area with spacious 15 x 35 ft inground pool.  Amazingly cute and modern home.
